description:
Have only completed a minute, but I've nonetheless vastly improved the initial revision. 

- Although I'm unsure as to what tuning D666 used on "Terror Abraxas", they typically play in D#/Eb so I switched the tab to that.
- Added distortion guitars/drums, plus credits where they're due.
- Switched acoustic guitars to clean
- Adjusted BPM and timing
title: Trialed By Fire
